        <exercise id="fs-id2639547" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1901135">    <para id="import-auto-id3115592">(a) What is the mass of a deep breath of air having a volume of 2.00 L? (b) Discuss the effect taking such a breath has on your body’s volume and density.</para>
